document.name: Berkely
document.description: The Berkely handbag features a structured silhouette with a sophisticated flap closure and silver-tone turn lock. Crafted from premium suede and leather in a versatile grey tone, this elegant bag includes a top handle and detachable shoulder strap for multiple carrying options.
document.material:
Suede and leather combination with textile lining. Metal hardware with silver-tone finish.
- Avoid exposure to moisture and direct sunlight
Store in the provided dust bag when not in use
Clean suede with a specialized suede brush
Treat leather portions with appropriate leather conditioner
